OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1777669904
OL,3,C25 people have been charged with
OL,4,Cpublic order offences after raids in
OL,5,CCrewe
OL,7,F25 people have been charged with
OL,8,Fpublic order offences after police
OL,9,Fraided a religious group in Crewe.
OL,11,FDetectives say the charges do not
OL,12,Frelate to the investigation into
OL,13,Fallegations of sexual abuse, forced
OL,14,Fmarriage and people trafficking.
OL,16,FTen other people were also arrested
OL,17,Fand remain in police custody.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
