OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1777669904
OL,3,C25 people have been charged with
OL,4,Cpublic order offences after raids in
OL,5,CCrewe
OL,7,FOn Wednesday, more than 500 officers
OL,8,Fstormed three locations linked to the
OL,9,FAhmadi Religion of Peace and Light,
OL,10,Fincluding the headquarters on Victoria
OL,11,FAvenue.
OL,13,FCheshire Police said the alleged
OL,14,Foffences involved one victim, a woman,
OL,15,Fwho was a member of the group at the
OL,16,Ftime the offences occurred.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
