PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1777669904
OL,3,C25 people have been charged with
OL,4,Cpublic order offences after raids in
OL,5,CCrewe
OL,7,FThe Ahmadi religious community, which
OL,8,Fis said to be linked to a branch of
OL,9,FIslam, are based at a former
OL,10,Forphanage, Webb House, with around 150
OL,11,Fpeople living at the property.
OL,13,FChief Superintendent Gareth Wrigley
OL,14,Fsaid: "Our policing activity and
OL,15,Fongoing, complex investigation relates
OL,16,Fto allegations of serious sexual
OL,17,Foffences, forced marriage and modern
OL,18,Fslavery."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
